{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853709975,"sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","part":{"id":"prt_d79212a730010GoLn0oCpsT9tE","messageID":"msg_d792123d1001F5gAKikVoXjSu2","sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-22f85b02465c4dcf8705dd669eaed76c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010 — Router 会话管理\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/router`\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ## SessionManager 接口定义\n8: \n9: ### 场景: 定义 SessionManager 接口\n10: \n11: **GIVEN** 需要管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的会话生命周期\n12: **WHEN** 定义 SessionManager 接口\n13: **THEN** 在 `session_manager.go` 中定义接口方法\n14: \n15: ```go\n16: type SessionManager interface {\n17:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n18:     CreateSession(ctx context.Context, name string, namespace string, kind string) (string, *types.SandboxInfo, error)\n19: }\n20: ```\n21: \n22: ## SessionManager 初始化\n23: \n24: ### 场景: 创建 SessionManager 实例\n25: \n26: **GIVEN** 有可用的 store client 和 workload manager 地址\n27: **WHEN** 调用 NewSessionManager\n28: **THEN** 返回初始化好的 SessionManager 实例\n29: \n30: ```go\n31: func NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store, workloadMgrAddr string) (SessionManager, error)\n32: ```\n33: \n34: ### 场景: 验证必需参数\n35: \n36: **GIVEN** 创建 SessionManager\n37: **WHEN** store client 为 nil 或 workload manager 地址为空\n38: **THEN** 返回错误\n39: \n40: ```go\n41: if storeClient == nil {\n42:     return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"store client is required\")\n43: }\n44: \n45: if workloadMgrAddr == \"\" {\n46:     return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"workload manager address is required\")\n47: }\n48: ```\n49: \n50: ## 会话创建\n51: \n52: ### 场景: 创建新的 AgentRuntime 会话\n53: \n54: **GIVEN** 用户请求调用 AgentRuntime\n55: **WHEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 kind 为 AgentRuntimeKind\n56: **THEN** 向 WorkloadManager 创建会话并返回会话 ID 和沙箱信息\n57: \n58: ```go\n59: sessionID, sandboxInfo, err := sessionManager.CreateSession(ctx, \"my-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n60: ```\n61: \n62: ### 场景: 创建新的 CodeInterpreter 会话\n63: \n64: **GIVEN** 用户请求调用 CodeInterpreter\n65: **WHEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 kind 为 CodeInterpreterKind\n66: **THEN** 向 WorkloadManager 创建会话并返回会话 ID 和沙箱信息\n67: \n68: ```go\n69: sessionID, sandboxInfo, err := sessionManager.CreateSession(ctx, \"my-interpreter\", \"default\", types.CodeInterpreterKind)\n70: ```\n71: \n72: ### 场景: 验证 Kind 类型\n73: \n74: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n75: **WHEN** kind 不是 AgentRuntimeKind 或 CodeInterpreterKind\n76: **THEN** 返回验证错误\n77: \n78: ```go\n79: func validateKind(kind string) error {\n80:     if kind != types.AgentRuntimeKind && kind != types.CodeInterpreterKind {\n81:         return fmt.Errorf(\"invalid kind: %s, must be %s or %s\", kind, types.AgentRuntimeKind, types.CodeInterpreterKind)\n82:     }\n83:     return nil\n84: }\n85: ```\n86: \n87: ### 场景: 验证命名空间格式\n88: \n89: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n90: **WHEN** namespace 格式无效\n91: **THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n92: \n93: ```go\n94: func isValidNamespace(namespace string) bool {\n95:     if namespace == \"\" {\n96:         return false\n97:     }\n98:     if len(namespace) > 63 {\n99:         return false\n100:     }\n101:     return namespaceRegex.MatchString(namespace)\n102: }\n103: ```\n104: \n105: ### 场景: 验证资源名称格式\n106: \n107: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n108: **WHEN** name 格式无效\n109: **THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n110: \n111: ```go\n112: func isValidResourceName(name string) bool {\n113:     if name == \"\" {\n114:         return false\n115:     }\n116:     if len(name) > 253 {\n117:         return false\n118:     }\n119:     return resourceNameRegex.MatchString(name)\n120: }\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ### 场景: 构造 WorkloadManager 请求\n124: \n125: **GIVEN** 创建会话的参数已验证\n126: **WHEN** 构造 HTTP 请求到 WorkloadManager\n127: **THEN** 根据 kind 选择正确的 endpoint\n128: \n129: ```go\n130: if kind == types.AgentRuntimeKind {\n131:     endpoint = fmt.Sprintf(\"%s/v1/agent-runtime\", m.workloadMgrAddr)\n132: } else {\n133:     endpoint = fmt.Sprintf(\"%s/v1/code-interpreter\", m.workloadMgrAddr)\n134: }\n135: ```\n136: \n137: ### 场景: 处理 WorkloadManager 创建成功\n138: \n139: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 200 OK\n140: **WHEN** 解析响应\n141: **THEN** 提取 sessionID 并查询完整沙箱信息\n142: \n143: ```go\n144: var createResp WorkloadManagerCreateResponse\n145: if err := json.Unmarshal(body, &createResp); err != nil {\n146:     return \"\", nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to unmarshal create response: %w\", err)\n147: }\n148: \n149: sessionID := createResp.SessionID\n150: ```\n151: \n152: ### 场景: 处理 WorkloadManager 创建失败\n153: \n154: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回非 200 状态码\n155: **WHEN** 创建会话失败\n156: **THEN** 返回 WorkloadManagerError\n157: \n158: ```go\n159: if resp.StatusCode != http.StatusOK {\n160:     return \"\", nil, &WorkloadManagerError{\n161:         Message: string(body),\n162:         Code:    resp.StatusCode,\n163:     }\n164: }\n165: ```\n166: \n167: ## 会话查询\n168: \n169: ### 场景: 从缓存获取会话\n170: \n171: **GIVEN** 会话已存在于 Redis 缓存\n172: **WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n173: **THEN** 从 store 返回沙箱信息，记录缓存命中\n174: \n175: ```go\n176: func (m *manager) GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error) {\n177:     sandboxInfo, err := m.storeClient.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)\n178:     if err == nil {\n179:         klog.V(4).Infof(\"Cache hit for session: %s\", sessionID)\n180:         return sandboxInfo, nil\n181:     }\n182:     // ...\n183: }\n184: ```\n185: \n186: ### 场景: 缓存未命中时查询 WorkloadManager\n187: \n188: **GIVEN** 会话不在 Redis 缓存中\n189: **WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n190: **THEN** 向 WorkloadManager 查询会话信息\n191: \n192: ```go\n193: if err != nil {\n194:     if err == store.ErrNotFound {\n195:         klog.V(4).Infof(\"Cache miss for session: %s, querying workload manager\", sessionID)\n196:         return m.getSandboxFromWorkloadManager(ctx, sessionID)\n197:     }\n198:     // ...\n199: }\n200: ```\n201: \n202: ### 场景: WorkloadManager 查询成功并缓存\n203: \n204: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回会话信息\n205: **WHEN** 查询成功\n206: **THEN** 将沙箱信息存入 Redis 缓存\n207: \n208: ```go\n209: sandboxInfo := SandboxInfoFromWorkloadManager(&getSessionResp, sessionID)\n210: \n211: if err := m.storeClient.StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n212:     klog.Warningf(\"Failed to cache sandbox info: %v\", err)\n213: }\n214: \n215: return sandboxInfo, nil\n216: ```\n217: \n218: ### 场景: WorkloadManager 返回 404\n219: \n220: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 404 Not Found\n221: **WHEN** 查询会话\n222: **THEN** 返回 SandboxNotFoundError\n223: \n224: ```go\n225: if resp.StatusCode == http.StatusNotFound {\n226:     return nil, &SandboxNotFoundError{SessionID: sessionID}\n227: }\n228: ```\n229: \n230: ### 场景: WorkloadManager 返回其他错误\n231: \n232: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回非 200 和非 404 状态码\n233: **WHEN** 查询会话失败\n234: **THEN** 返回 WorkloadManagerError\n235: \n236: ```go\n237: if resp.StatusCode != http.StatusOK {\n238:     return nil, &WorkloadManagerError{\n239:         Message: string(body),\n240:         Code:    resp.StatusCode,\n241:     }\n242: }\n243: ```\n244: \n245: ## 类型转换\n246: \n247: ### 场景: 转换 WorkloadManager 响应为 SandboxInfo\n248: \n249: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回会话响应\n250: **WHEN** 转换为内部类型\n251: **THEN** 正确映射所有字段\n252: \n253: ```go\n254: func SandboxInfoFromWorkloadManager(resp *WorkloadManagerGetSessionResponse, sessionID string) *types.SandboxInfo {\n255:     createdAt, _ := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, resp.CreatedAt)\n256:     expiresAt, _ := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, resp.ExpiresAt)\n257:     lastActivity, _ := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, resp.LastActivity)\n258: \n259:     return &types.SandboxInfo{\n260:         Kind:             resp.Kind,\n261:         SandboxID:        resp.SandboxID,\n262:         SandboxName:      resp.SandboxName,\n263:         SandboxNamespace: resp.Namespace,\n264:         Name:             resp.Name,\n265:         EntryPoints:      resp.EntryPoints,\n266:         SessionID:        sessionID,\n267:         CreatedAt:        createdAt,\n268:         ExpiresAt:        expiresAt,\n269:         Status:           \"Ready\",\n270:         PodIP:            resp.PodIP,\n271:         Namespace:        resp.Namespace,\n272:         LastActivityAt:   lastActivity,\n273:     }\n274: }\n275: ```\n276: \n277: ## 错误处理\n278: \n279: ### 场景: 处理存储错误\n280: \n281: **GIVEN** Redis 操作失败\n282: **WHEN** 发生存储错误\n283: **THEN** 记录警告日志，不阻断流程\n284: \n285: ```go\n286: if err := m.storeClient.StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n287:     klog.Warningf(\"Failed to cache sandbox info: %v\", err)\n288: }\n289: ```\n290: \n291: ### 场景: 处理 HTTP 超时\n292: \n293: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 响应超时\n294: **WHEN** HTTP 调用超时\n295: **THEN** 返回服务不可用错误\n296: \n297: ```go\n298: httpClient: &http.Client{Timeout: 30 * time.Second}\n299: ```\n300: \n301: ### 场景: 处理 JSON 解析错误\n302: \n303: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回无效 JSON\n304: **WHEN** 解析响应失败\n305: **THEN** 返回格式化错误\n306: \n307: ```go\n308: if err := json.Unmarshal(body, &createResp); err != nil {\n309:     return \"\", nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to unmarshal create response: %w\", err)\n310: }\n311: ```\n312: \n313: ## 测试场景\n314: \n315: ### 场景: 测试缓存命中\n316: \n317: **GIVEN** 会话存在于 Redis\n318: **WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n319: **THEN** 直接从 Redis 返回，不调用 WorkloadManager\n320: \n321: ```go\n322: func TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_CacheHit(t *testing.T) {\n323:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n324:     expectedSandbox := &types.SandboxInfo{\n325:         SessionID: \"test-session\",\n326:         SandboxID: \"test-sandbox\",\n327:     }\n328:     mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(expectedSandbox, nil)\n329: \n330:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n331: \n332:     result, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"test-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n333: \n334:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n335:     assert.Equal(t, expectedSandbox, result)\n336:     mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n337: }\n338: ```\n339: \n340: ### 场景: 测试缓存未命中并回源\n341: \n342: **GIVEN** 会话不存在于 Redis\n343: **WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n344: **THEN** 调用 WorkloadManager 并缓存结果\n345: \n346: ```go\n347: func TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_CacheMiss(t *testing.T) {\n348:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n349:     mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n350:     expectedSandbox := &types.SandboxInfo{\n351:         SessionID: \"test-session\",\n352:         SandboxID: \"test-sandbox\",\n353:     }\n354: \n355:     mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(nil, store.ErrNotFound)\n356:     mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\", mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n357: \n358:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n359:     sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n360: \n361:     result, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"test-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n362: \n363:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n364:     assert.Equal(t, expectedSandbox.SandboxID, result.SandboxID)\n365:     mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n366: }\n367: ```\n368: \n369: ### 场景: 测试创建会话成功\n370: \n371: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且所有参数有效\n372: **WHEN** WorkloadManager 成功创建会话\n373: **THEN** 返回 sessionID 和沙箱信息\n374: \n375: ```go\n376: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession_Success(t *testing.T) {\n377:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n378:     mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n379: \n380:     createResponse := &WorkloadManagerCreateResponse{\n381:         SessionID:   \"new-session-id\",\n382:         SandboxID:   \"new-sandbox-id\",\n383:         SandboxName: \"test-agent\",\n384:         EntryPoints: []types.SandboxEntryPoint{{Path: \"/\", Port: 8080}},\n385:     }\n386: \n387:     getSessionResponse := &WorkloadManagerGetSessionResponse{\n388:         SessionID:    \"new-session-id\",\n389:         SandboxID:    \"new-sandbox-id\",\n390:         SandboxName:  \"test-agent\",\n391:         Kind:         types.AgentRuntimeKind,\n392:         Namespace:    \"default\",\n393:         Name:         \"test-agent\",\n394:         EntryPoints:  []types.SandboxEntryPoint{{Path: \"/\", Port: 8080}},\n395:         LastActivity: time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n396:         CreatedAt:    time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n397:         ExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour).Format(time.RFC3339),\n398:     }\n399: \n400:     mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"new-session-id\", mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n401:     mockHTTPClient.SetupCreateResponse(200, createResponse)\n402:     mockHTTPClient.SetupGetSessionResponse(200, getSessionResponse)\n403: \n404:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n405:     sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n406: \n407:     sessionID, sandboxInfo, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n408: \n409:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n410:     assert.Equal(t, \"new-session-id\", sessionID)\n411:     assert.Equal(t, \"new-sandbox-id\", sandboxInfo.SandboxID)\n412: }\n413: ```\n414: \n415: ### 场景: 测试无效 Kind\n416: \n417: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 kind 无效\n418: **WHEN** kind 不是 AgentRuntimeKind 或 CodeInterpreterKind\n419: **THEN** 返回验证错误\n420: \n421: ```go\n422: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession_InvalidKind(t *testing.T) {\n423:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n424:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n425: \n426:     _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", \"InvalidKind\")\n427: \n428:     assert.Error(t, err)\n429:     assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"invalid kind\")\n430: }\n431: ```\n432: \n433: ### 场景: 测试无效命名空间\n434: \n435: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 namespace 格式无效\n436: **WHEN** namespace 包含大写字母\n437: **THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n438: \n439: ```go\n440: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession_InvalidNamespace(t *testing.T) {\n441:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n442:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n443: \n444:     _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"InvalidNamespace\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n445: \n446:     assert.Error(t, err)\n447:     _, ok := err.(*ValidationError)\n448:     assert.True(t, ok)\n449:     assert.Equal(t, \"namespace\", err.(*ValidationError).Field)\n450: }\n451: ```\n452: \n453: ### 场景: 测试无效资源名称\n454: \n455: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 name 格式无效\n456: **WHEN** name 超过长度限制\n457: **THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n458: \n459: ```go\n460: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession_InvalidName(t *testing.T) {\n461:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n462:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n463: \n464:     longName := strings.Repeat(\"a\", 254)\n465:     _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), longName, \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n466: \n467:     assert.Error(t, err)\n468:     _, ok := err.(*ValidationError)\n469:     assert.True(t, ok)\n470:     assert.Equal(t, \"name\", err.(*ValidationError).Field)\n471: }\n472: ```\n473: \n474: ### 场景: 测试 WorkloadManager 创建失败\n475: \n476: **GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n477: **WHEN** WorkloadManager 返回 500 错误\n478: **THEN** 返回 WorkloadManagerError\n479: \n480: ```go\n481: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession_WorkloadManagerError(t *testing.T) {\n482:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n483:     mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n484: \n485:     mockHTTPClient.SetupCreateResponse(500, nil)\n486: \n487:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n488:     sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n489: \n490:     _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n491: \n492:     assert.Error(t, err)\n493:     _, ok := err.(*WorkloadManagerError)\n494:     assert.True(t, ok)\n495: }\n496: ```\n497: \n498: ### 场景: 测试会话未找到\n499: \n500: **GIVEN** 查询不存在的会话\n501: **WHEN** WorkloadManager 返回 404\n502: **THEN** 返回 SandboxNotFoundError\n503: \n504: ```go\n505: func TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_NotFound(t *testing.T) {\n506:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n507:     mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n508: \n509:     mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"nonexistent-session\").Return(nil, store.ErrNotFound)\n510:     mockHTTPClient.SetupGetSessionResponse(404, nil)\n511: \n512:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n513:     sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n514: \n515:     _, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"nonexistent-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n516: \n517:     assert.Error(t, err)\n518:     _, ok := err.(*SandboxNotFoundError)\n519:     assert.True(t, ok)\n520: }\n521: ```\n522: \n523: ### 场景: 测试存储失败降级\n524: \n525: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回会话信息但 Redis 失败\n526: **WHEN** 缓存操作失败\n527: **THEN** 仍返回会话信息，记录警告\n528: \n529: ```go\n530: func TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_StoreFailure(t *testing.T) {\n531:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n532:     mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n533: \n534:     getSessionResponse := &WorkloadManagerGetSessionResponse{\n535:         SessionID:    \"test-session\",\n536:         SandboxID:    \"test-sandbox\",\n537:         SandboxName:  \"test-agent\",\n538:         Kind:         types.AgentRuntimeKind,\n539:         Namespace:    \"default\",\n540:         Name:         \"test-agent\",\n541:         EntryPoints:  []types.SandboxEntryPoint{{Path: \"/\", Port: 8080}},\n542:         LastActivity: time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n543:         CreatedAt:    time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n544:         ExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour).Format(time.RFC3339),\n545:     }\n546: \n547:     mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(nil, store.ErrNotFound)\n548:     mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\", mock.Anything).Return(assert.AnError)\n549:     mockHTTPClient.SetupGetSessionResponse(200, getSessionResponse)\n550: \n551:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n552:     sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n553: \n554:     result, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"test-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n555: \n556:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n557:     assert.Equal(t, \"test-sandbox\", result.SandboxID)\n558: }\n559: ```\n560: \n561: ### 场景: 测试 HTTP 超时\n562: \n563: **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 响应缓慢\n564: **WHEN** HTTP 调用超时\n565: **THEN** 返回错误\n566: \n567: ```go\n568: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession_HTTPTimeout(t *testing.T) {\n569:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n570:     mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n571: \n572:     mockHTTPClient.SetupTimeout()\n573: \n574:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n575:     sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n576: \n577:     _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n578: \n579:     assert.Error(t, err)\n580:     assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"timeout\")\n581: }\n582: ```\n583: \n584: ## 配置\n585: \n586: ### 场景: 配置 WorkloadManager 地址\n587: \n588: **GIVEN** 需要连接到 WorkloadManager\n589: **WHEN** 初始化 SessionManager\n590: **THEN** 通过构造函数传入 WorkloadManager 地址\n591: \n592: ```go\n593: workloadMgrAddr := \"http://workload-manager:8080\"\n594: sm, err := NewSessionManager(storeClient, workloadMgrAddr)\n595: ```\n596: \n597: ### 场景: 配置 HTTP 超时\n598: \n599: **GIVEN** 需要控制 HTTP 超时时间\n600: **WHEN** 创建 HTTP 客户端\n601: **THEN** 设置合理的超时值\n602: \n603: ```go\n604: httpClient: &http.Client{Timeout: 30 * time.Second}\n605: ```\n606: \n607: ## 集成测试\n608: \n609: ### 场景: 端到端会话创建和查询\n610: \n611: **GIVEN** 启动完整的 Router 服务\n612: **WHEN** 发送创建会话请求\n613: **THEN** 会话成功创建并可查询\n614: \n615: ```go\n616: func TestE2E_SessionCreation(t *testing.T) {\n617:     // 1. 启动 WorkloadManager mock\n618:     // 2. 启动 Redis\n619:     // 3. 创建 SessionManager\n620:     // 4. 调用 CreateSession\n621:     // 5. 验证返回\n622:     // 6. 使用 sessionID 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n623:     // 7. 验证缓存命中\n624: }\n625: ```\n626: \n627: ### 场景: 并发会话创建\n628: \n629: **GIVEN** 多个并发请求创建会话\n630: **WHEN** 同时调用 CreateSession\n631: **THEN** 所有会话成功创建且 sessionID 唯一\n632: \n633: ```go\n634: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession_Concurrent(t *testing.T) {\n635:     mockStore := &mockStore{}\n636:     mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n637: \n638:     sessionIDs := make(map[string]bool)\n639:     var mu sync.Mutex\n640: \n641:     sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n642: \n643:     var wg sync.WaitGroup\n644:     for i := 0; i < 10; i++ {\n645:         wg.Add(1)\n646:         go func(n int) {\n647:             defer wg.Done()\n648:             sessionID, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), fmt.Sprintf(\"agent-%d\", n), \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n649:             assert.NoError(t, err)\n650: \n651:             mu.Lock()\n652:             defer mu.Unlock()\n653:             assert.False(t, sessionIDs[sessionID], \"duplicate session ID: %s\", sessionID)\n654:             sessionIDs[sessionID] = true\n655:         }(i)\n656:     }\n657: \n658:     wg.Wait()\n659:     assert.Equal(t, 10, len(sessionIDs))\n660: }\n661: ```\n662: \n663: ## 验收标准\n664: \n665: ### 场景: 验证会话创建成功率\n666: \n667: **GIVEN** 大量创建会话请求\n668: **WHEN** 统计成功率\n669: **THEN** 成功率 > 99%\n670: \n671: ### 场景: 验证缓存命中率\n672: \n673: **GIVEN** 多次查询同一会话\n674: **WHEN** 统计缓存命中\n675: **THEN** 缓存命中率 > 90%\n676: \n677: ### 场景: 验证查询延迟\n678: \n679: **GIVEN** 缓存命中场景\n680: **WHEN** 测量查询延迟\n681: **THEN** P99 延迟 < 10ms\n682: \n683: ### 场景: 验证零会话冲突\n684: \n685: **GIVEN** 大量并发会话创建\n686: **WHEN** 检查 sessionID\n687: **THEN** 无重复 sessionID\n688: \n689: ## 文件组织\n690: \n691: ### 场景: 文件结构清晰\n692: \n693: **GIVEN** pkg/router 模块组织代码\n694: **WHEN** 创建文件结构\n695: **THEN** 按职责分离文件：\n696: \n697: ```\n698: pkg/router/\n699: ├── session_manager.go       # SessionManager 核心实现\n700: ├── session_manager_test.go  # 单元测试\n701: ├── handlers.go              # HTTP 处理器\n702: ├── middleware.go            # 中间件\n703: ├── jwt.go                   # JWT 管理\n704: ├── proxy.go                 # 反向代理\n705: ├── server.go                # HTTP 服务器\n706: ├── config.go                # 配置\n707: ├── types.go                 # 类型定义\n708: ├── errors.go                # 错误定义\n709: ├── utils.go                 # 工具函数\n710: └── doc.go                   # 包文档\n711: ```\n\n(End of file - total 711 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010 — Router 会话管理\n\n**Module:** `pkg/router`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** M\n\n## SessionManager 接口定义\n\n### 场景: 定义 SessionManager 接口\n\n**GIVEN** 需要管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的会话生命周期\n**WHEN** 定义 SessionManager 接口\n**THEN** 在 `session_manager.go` 中定义接口方法\n\n```go\ntype SessionManager interface {\n    GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    CreateSession(ctx context.Context, name string, namespace string, kind string) (string, *types.SandboxInfo, error)\n}\n```","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775853709964,"end":1775853709972}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775853710000,"sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","part":{"id":"prt_d79212a96001qV5N2sDzaonPXz","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d792123d1001F5gAKikVoXjSu2","sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":25214,"input":381,"output":66,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":24767}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775853714083,"sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","part":{"id":"prt_d79213aa0001A298RdvM184sSA","messageID":"msg_d79212ac6001FCVR7pkopxphLB","sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853746594,"sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","part":{"id":"prt_d7921b90b001EZSgWUWmI55RGG","messageID":"msg_d79212ac6001FCVR7pkopxphLB","sessionID":"ses_286df542bffeaJTMMuyEk1U0LY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-308babc3190e4799b24d51c80ae8c1ea","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# delta-spec.md — AR-013: Redis 存储实现\n\n## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\n\n## Delta Overview\n\n新增 Redis/Valkey 后端实现，用于持久化 sandbox 元数据。支持按 session ID 存储、检索、更新和删除，并提供基于过期时间和最后活动时间的索引查询。\n\n---\n\n## 新增接口和类型\n\n### Requirement: Store interface contract\n\n系统 SHALL 提供 `Store` 接口，由 Redis 和 Valkey 提供商实现。\n\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n    GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n    ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n    Close() error\n}\n```\n\n### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\n\n- **GIVEN** 一个健康的 Redis/Valkey 服务器\n- **WHEN** 调用 `Ping(ctx)`\n- **THEN** 实现发送 PING 命令并要求返回字符串 `PONG`\n\n---\n\n## 错误处理\n\n### Requirement: Not found semantics\n\n系统 SHALL 返回包级错误 `ErrNotFound`（消息 `store: not found`），当 session key 在读取时不存在，或最后活动时间更新指向缺失的 session 时。\n\n```go\nvar ErrNotFound = errors.New(\"store: not found\")\n```\n\n### Scenario: Get missing session\n\n- **GIVEN** 后端不存在 key `session:{id}`\n- **WHEN** 执行 `GetSandboxBySessionID`\n- **THEN** 错误为 `ErrNotFound`（Redis: `Nil`；Valkey: `IsValkeyNil`）\n\n---\n\n## 数据存储键设计\n\n### Requirement: Session key naming\n\n系统 SHALL 使用字符串前缀 `session:` 与 session id 拼接作为 JSON 文档存储的主键。\n\n### Scenario: Key construction\n\n- **GIVEN** session id `abc`\n- **WHEN** 存储写入 sandbox 数据\n- **THEN** 字符串 key 为 `session:abc`\n\n---\n\n## 索引设计\n\n### Requirement: Expiry index\n\n系统 SHALL 维护有序集合 key `session:expiry`，成员为 session id，分数为 `ExpiresAt` Unix 秒数。`StoreSandbox` SHALL 添加成员并使用 sandbox 过期分数。`DeleteSandboxBySessionID` SHALL 删除成员。\n\n### Scenario: List expired uses ZRANGEBYSCORE\n\n- **GIVEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)` 且 limit > 0\n- **WHEN** 实现查询索引\n- **THEN** 选择分数从负无穷到 `before.Unix()` 的成员，限制为 `limit` 条\n\n### Requirement: Last-activity index\n\n系统 SHALL 维护有序集合 key `session:last_activity`，成员为 session id，分数为最后活动 Unix 秒数。`StoreSandbox` SHALL ZADD 分数为 `time.Now().Unix()`。`UpdateSessionLastActivity` SHALL ZADD 提供的时间戳（或零时使用当前时间）。`DeleteSandboxBySessionID` SHALL ZREM 成员。\n\n### Scenario: List inactive uses activity index\n\n- **GIVEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)`\n- **WHEN** 执行\n- **THEN** 返回最后活动分数 ≤ `before.Unix()` 的成员，最多 `limit` 条\n\n---\n\n## 存储操作\n\n### Requirement: StoreSandbox atomicity and validation\n\n系统 SHALL 拒绝 nil sandbox 或零 `ExpiresAt`。系统 SHALL 在一个 pipeline/multi 块中执行 session key 的 SETNX、ZADD expiry 和 ZADD last_activity。系统 SHALL 如果批处理中任何命令错误则失败。\n\n### Scenario: Nil sandbox rejected\n\n- **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, nil)`\n- **WHEN** 调用\n- **THEN** 错误指示 sandbox 为 nil\n\n---\n\n## 更新操作\n\n### Requirement: UpdateSandbox semantics\n\n系统 SHALL 仅使用 SET with XX（key 必须存在）更新 session JSON 值。系统 SHALL 在此操作中不修改 expiry 或 last-activity ZSET 条目。\n\n### Scenario: Missing key on update\n\n- **GIVEN** session key 不存在\n- **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox` 运行\n- **THEN** Redis: SETXX 返回 false → 错误 `key not exists`；Valkey: 响应非 OK → 同类错误\n\n---\n\n## 删除操作\n\n### Requirement: DeleteSandboxBySessionID cleanup\n\n系统 SHALL 在一个 pipeline/multi 中删除 session key 并从两个有序集合中移除 session id。\n\n### Scenario: Full removal\n\n- **GIVEN** 一个存在的 session\n- **WHEN** 删除成功\n- **THEN** GET session key 返回 not found，ZSET 不再包含该成员\n\n---\n\n## 查询操作\n\n### Requirement: List loaders tolerate missing keys\n\n当按 ZSET 列出返回 session id 时，系统 SHALL 按 id 加载 JSON；如果字符串 key 缺失 SHALL 跳过条目（Redis pipeline GET nil，Valkey MGET 空字符串）而不导致整个批处理失败。\n\n### Scenario: Orphan ZSET member\n\n- **GIVEN** ZSET 中的 session id 没有对应的 hash/string 值\n- **WHEN** `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` 运行\n- **THEN** 该 id 从返回的 slice 中省略\n\n---\n\n## 活动更新\n\n### Requirement: UpdateSessionLastActivity preconditions\n\n系统 SHALL 拒绝空 session id。如果 `at` 为零时间，系统 SHALL 使用 `time.Now()`。系统 SHALL 在 ZADD 前验证 session key 存在；如果不存在 SHALL 返回 `ErrNotFound`。\n\n### Scenario: Activity bump for unknown session\n\n- **GIVEN** 没有 `session:{id}` key\n- **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity`\n- **THEN** 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n\n---\n\n## 后端选择\n\n### Requirement: Provider selection via STORE_TYPE\n\n系统 SHALL 不区分大小写读取 `STORE_TYPE`；如果未设置 SHALL 默认为 `redis`。支持的值 SHALL 为 `redis` 和 `valkey`；任何其他值 SHALL 导致初始化失败。\n\n```go\nconst (\n    redisStoreType  string = \"redis\"\n    valkeyStoreType string = \"valkey\"\n)\n```\n\n### Scenario: Default redis\n\n- **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` 未设置\n- **WHEN** `Storage()` 首次初始化\n- **THEN** Redis 实现被构造\n\n---\n\n## Redis 配置\n\n### Requirement: Redis environment and password policy\n\n系统 SHALL 要求 `REDIS_ADDR`。系统 SHALL 要求非空 `REDIS_PASSWORD`，除非 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 不区分大小写设置为 false。\n\n### Scenario: Password required by default\n\n- **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` 设置且 `REDIS_PASSWORD` 为空且 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 未设置\n- **WHEN** Redis store 初始化\n- **THEN** 初始化失败，错误提示需要密码\n\n---\n\n## Valkey 配置\n\n### Requirement: Valkey environment and options\n\n系统 SHALL 要求 `VALKEY_ADDR`（逗号分隔的地址拆分为 `InitAddress`）。系统 SHALL 要求非空 `VALKEY_PASSWORD`，除非 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`。系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` 解析为 true 时设置 `DisableCache` 为 true；系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` 解析为 true 时设置 `ForceSingleClient` 为 true。\n\n### Scenario: Optional client flags\n\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true`\n- **WHEN** Valkey client options 被构建\n- **THEN** `ClientOption` 上的 `DisableCache` 为 true\n\n---\n\n## 单例访问\n\n### Requirement: Singleton access\n\n系统 SHALL 使用 `sync.Once` 暴露 `func Storage() Store`；失败的 init SHALL 通过 klog 记录 fatal。\n\n```go\nfunc Storage() Store\nfunc initStore() error\n```\n\n### Scenario: Single initialization\n\n- **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 调用 `Storage()`\n- **WHEN** 它们并发运行\n- **THEN** `initStore` 恰好执行一次\n\n---\n\n## 存储的数据结构\n\n### SandboxInfo 结构体\n\n```go\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n    SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n    Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n    EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n    SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n    Status           string              `json:\"status\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n    Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n    Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n    Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Redis 实现细节\n\n### Requirement: RedisStore struct\n\nRedis 实现 SHALL 使用 `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` 客户端。\n\n```go\ntype redisStore struct {\n    cli                  *redisv9.Client\n    sessionPrefix        string\n    expiryIndexKey       string\n    lastActivityIndexKey string\n}\n```\n\n### Requirement: Fixed key patterns\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|--------|\n| `sessionPrefix` | `\"session:\"` |\n| `expiryIndexKey` | `\"session:expiry\"` |\n| `lastActivityIndexKey` | `\"session:last_activity\"` |\n\n### Scenario: Redis operations summary\n\n| Method | Redis commands |\n|--------|----------------|\n| `Ping` | `PING` → expect `PONG` |\n| `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `GET session:{id}` |\n| `StoreSandbox` | Pipeline: `SETNX`, `ZADD session:expiry`, `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n| `UpdateSandbox` | `SET key value XX` |\n| `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | Pipeline: `DEL`, `ZREM expiry`, `ZREM last_activity` |\n| `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:expiry -inf {before.Unix} LIMIT 0 limit` then pipeline GETs |\n| `ListInactiveSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:last_activity ...` then pipeline GETs |\n| `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `GET` (existence), then `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n| `Close` | `cli.Close()` |\n\n---\n\n## Valkey 实现细节\n\n### Requirement: ValkeyStore struct\n\nValkey 实现 SHALL 使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端。\n\n```go\ntype valkeyStore struct {\n    cli                  valkey.Client\n    sessionPrefix        string\n    expiryIndexKey       string\n    lastActivityIndexKey string\n}\n```\n\n### Scenario: Valkey operations summary\n\n| Method | Valkey API |\n|--------|------------|\n| `Ping` | `B().Ping()` → string `PONG` |\n| `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `B().Get().Key(key)` → bytes; `IsValkeyNil` → `ErrNotFound` |\n| `StoreSandbox` | `DoMulti`: `SETNX`, `ZADD` expiry, `ZADD` last_activity |\n| `UpdateSandbox` | `SET ... XX`; success requires `ToString() == \"OK\"` |\n| `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | `DoMulti`: `DEL`, `ZREM` expiry, `ZREM` last_activity |\n| `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `Zrangebyscore` with `Min(\"-inf\")`, `Max(fmt.Sprintf(\"%d\", before.Unix()))`, `Limit(0, limit)` |\n| `ListInactiveSandboxes` | Same on `last_activity` key |\n| `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `Exists` key → int64 must be 1; then `Zadd` |\n| `Close` | `vs.cli.Close()` then return nil |\n\n---\n\n## 依赖项\n\n### Requirement: Package imports\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"time\"\n    \"sync\"\n\n    \"github.com/redis/go-redis/v9\"\n    \"github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go\"\n    \"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n)\n```","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775853746514,"end":1775853746592}}}}
